## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-114">このコンストラクターは、含んでいる文法内の <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> オブジェクトへの規則参照を作成します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-114">This constructor creates a rule reference to an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object within the containing  grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-115">外部文法ファイルの `rule` 要素へのルール参照を作成するには、次のいずれかのコンストラクターを使用します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-115">To create a rule reference to a `rule` element in an external grammar file, use any of the following constructors:</span></span>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%2A>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%2A>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%2A>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%29>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-116">次の例では、"ワールドカップを獲得した国" という語句を認識する文法を作成し、その後にワールドカップを獲得した国の名前が続きます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-116">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-117"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> オブジェクト `winnerRule` 作成し、文字列識別子 `WorldCupWinner`を指定すると、この例では、ルールに "ワールドカップを獲得した国" という文字列を追加します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-117">After creating the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object `winnerRule` and giving it the string identifier `WorldCupWinner`, the example appends the string  "A nation that has won the World Cup is" to the rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-118">この例では <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> オブジェクトを使用して、欧州の国/地域の一覧と南部の国/地域の一覧を作成し、それぞれの規則、`ruleEurope`、または `ruleSAmerica`に各リストを追加します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-118">Using <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> objects, the example then builds a list of European countries/regions and a list of South American countries/regions, and adds each list to its respective rule, `ruleEurope` or `ruleSAmerica`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-119">次に、`ruleEurope` と `ruleSAmerica` の規則の参照を作成し、それらを `WorldCupWinner` 規則に追加します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-119">The example then creates rule references for `ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica` and adds them to the `WorldCupWinner` rule.</span></span>  
  
```  
public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  
  
  // Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"),   
    new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"),   
    new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem   
    (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
  // Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
  // the root rule of the document.  
  document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  document.Root = winnerRule;  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-120">作成された文法には、次の形式があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-120">The created grammar has the following form.</span></span>  
  
```  
<grammar version="1.0" xml:lang="en-US" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2001/06/grammar" root="WorldCupWinner">  
    <rule id="WorldCupWinner" scope="public">  
        <item> A nation that has won the world cup is </item>  
        <one-of>  
            <item>  
                <ruleref uri="#EuropeanNations" />  
            </item>  
            <item>  
                <ruleref uri="#SouthAmericanNations" />  
            </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
    <rule id="EuropeanNations">  
        <one-of>  
            <item> England </item>  
            <item> France </item>  
            <item> Germany </item>  
            <item> Italy </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
    <rule id="SouthAmericanNations">  
        <one-of>  
            <item> Argentina </item>  
            <item> Brazil </item>  
            <item> Uruguay </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
</grammar>  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-125">このコンストラクターは、外部文法ファイルへの規則参照を作成します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-125">This constructor creates a rule reference to an external grammar file.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-126">URI には、`http://www.contoso.com/ExternalGrammar.grxml#targetRule`など、参照するルールの識別子を含めることもできます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-126">The URI may also include the identifier of a rule to reference, for example `http://www.contoso.com/ExternalGrammar.grxml#targetRule`.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-127">`uri` パラメーターで規則識別子が指定されていない場合、規則の参照は対象の文法のルート規則を指します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-127">If the `uri` parameter does not specify a rule identifier, the rule reference points to the root rule of the target grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-128">同じ文法内の <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> オブジェクトへのルール参照を作成するには、次のいずれかのコンストラクターを使用します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-128">To create a rule reference to an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object within the same grammar, use any of the following constructors:</span></span>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%2A>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%2A>  
  
-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef.%23ctor%2A>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-129">次の例では、バスシャトルサービスに関する情報を返すアプリケーションの文法を作成します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-129">The following example creates a grammar for an application that returns information about bus shuttle service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-130">最初のメソッドである `GrammarUrlForRoute`は、ルートを指定する文字列を受け取り、それを文法の場所を指定する文字列に追加します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-130">The first method, `GrammarUrlForRoute`, takes a string that specifies a route and appends it to a string specifying the location of a grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-131">これにより、その文法で特定のルールが指定されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-131">This specifies a particular rule in that grammar.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-132">メソッドは、その規則の `Uri` を返します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-132">The method returns a `Uri` for that rule.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-133">2番目のメソッド `CreateGrammarForRoute`は、`GrammarUrlForRoute`によって渡された `Uri` によって指定された規則参照を使用して、`grammar` という名前の <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> 要素を作成します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-133">The second method, `CreateGrammarForRoute`, creates an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> element named `grammar` with a rule reference specified by the `Uri` passed to it by `GrammarUrlForRoute`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-134">_Route という名前の変数は、外側のクラスのメンバーであることに注意してください。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-134">Note that the variable named _route is a member of an enclosing class.</span></span>  
  
```  
private Uri GrammarUrlForRoute(string route)  
{  
  return new Uri("http://localhost/MyBus/MyBusLocations.grxml#LocationsForRoute" + route);  
}  
  
private SrgsDocument CreateGrammarForRoute()  
{  
  SrgsDocument grammar = new SrgsDocument();  
  grammar.Mode = SrgsGrammarMode.Voice;  
  SrgsRule rule = new SrgsRule("LocationsForRoute" + _route);  
  SrgsRuleRef ruleref = new SrgsRuleRef(GrammarUrlForRoute(_route));  
  
  SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag tag = new SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag ("$.Location = $$");  
  
  rule.Elements.Add(ruleref);  
  rule.Elements.Add(tag);  
  grammar.Rules.Add(rule);  
  grammar.Root = rule;  
  return grammar;  
}  
```  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-135">前のサンプルでは、_`route` という名前の変数は宣言されていないため、未定義です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-135">The variable named _`route` is undeclared and undefined in the preceding sample.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7bc1a-136">これは、前のサンプルをコンパイルして実行する前に、<xref:System.String> として宣言し、特定のバスルートのルート番号を含める必要があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7bc1a-136">It should be declared as a <xref:System.String> and contain the route number for a particular bus route before the preceding sample is compiled and run.</span></span>

  
  
## Remarks  
